        <h1 class="fade-up fade-up-2">Parachute</h1>
        <p class="tagline fade-up fade-up-3">The note-taking system you've been looking for</p>
        <p class="subtitle fade-up fade-up-4">Voice-first &middot; Open source &middot; Works with any AI</p>
